description:
Meeting new open-minded friends on SpicyMatch is as easy as swiping right!
100% discretion & user privacy - YOU ARE IN TOTAL CONTROL!

The SpicyMatch App offers the following features:

•⁠  ⁠Full social media wall and news feed;
•⁠  ⁠Instant Messenger & Chat (without the need to give your mobile number out);
•⁠  ⁠Push Notifications - when someone views your profile, or you receive instant messages, or when people are looking to speed date, etc;
•⁠  ⁠Send & Accept Friends Requests and Like profiles on the fly;
•⁠  ⁠Speed Dating for immediate dates & Travel Plans of members travelling to your area;
•⁠  ⁠Parties, Vacations & Events right near you and all across the world;
•⁠  ⁠GPS Geolocation Map for members, shops, clubs, and points of interest, etc near you;
•⁠  ⁠Extensive advanced Search feature;
•⁠  ⁠Upload & share your photos directly from your device or use your camera to create new ones.

Regular Updates with new features. 
Please visit our website for all available features.
